#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Game Configuration</title>"
msgstr "<title>Mängu seadistamine</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:391
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kfourinline; can be configured using the configuration dialog with "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure "
#| "&kfourinline;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"
msgid ""
"&kfourinline; can be configured using the configuration dialog with the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kfourinline;…"
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"&kfourinline;'i saab seadistada seadistustedialoogis, mille avab menüükäsk "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu><guimenuitem>&kfourinline;'i "
"seadistamine...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Game Configuration</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Mängu seadistamine</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Starting Player Color</guilabel>: Determine which player color "
"(<guilabel>Red</guilabel> or <guilabel>Black</guilabel>) has the first move "
"in the next game."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Alustava mängija värv</guilabel>: määrab, millist värvi mängija "
"(<guilabel>Punane</guilabel> või <guilabel>Must</guilabel>) sooritab "
"järgmise mängu esimese käigu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Player Names</guilabel>: Change the names of the players."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Mängijate nimed</guilabel>: võimaldab muuta mängijate nimesid."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Black Plays With</guilabel>: Choose who should play for player 1. "
"It can be either <guilabel>Mouse</guilabel> or <guilabel>Keyboard</"
"guilabel>, &ie; a local player using the mouse or keyboard as input device "
"or <guilabel>Computer</guilabel>, &ie; the computer plays for this player."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Mustadega mängib</guilabel>: valib, kes mängib mängijat 1. See "
"võib olla kas <guimenuitem>hiir</guimenuitem> või <guimenuitem>klaviatuur</"
"guimenuitem>, &ie; kohalik mängija, kes kasutab sisendseadmena hiirt või "
"klaviatuuri, või <guimenuitem>arvuti</guimenuitem>, &ie; seda mängijat "
"mängib arvuti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:412
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Red Plays With</guilabel>: Same as <guilabel>Black Plays With</"
"guilabel> but for player 2 (red)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Punastega mängib</guilabel>: sama, mis <guimenuitem>Mustadega "
"mängib</guimenuitem>, ainult et mängija 2 (punane) kohta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Computer Difficulty</guilabel>: Select the level of the computer "
"player."
msgstr "<guilabel>Arvuti tase</guilabel>: valib arvutimängija taseme."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Use AI learning</guilabel>: The computer AI can learn from "
"mistakes made in one game."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>AI õppimine</guilabel>: arvuti AI õpib mängus tehtud vigadest."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Korduma kippuvad küsimused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I change the look of the game?"
msgstr "Kuidas muuta mängu välimust?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:430
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can change the color of the pieces by opening the <guimenu>Settings</"
#| "guimenu> menu and select <guisubmenu>Theme</guisubmenu>."
msgid ""
"You can change the color of the pieces by opening the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Theme</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Kivide värvi saab muuta, kui valida see menüü <guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu> "
"alammenüüst <guisubmenu>Teema</guisubmenu>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:438
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play the game?"
msgstr "Kas mängida saab ka klaviatuuri abil?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:443
#, no-c-format
msgid "You cannot use the keyboard to control the pieces."
msgstr "Kive ei saa klaviatuuri abil liigutada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid "I have lost control of who is in the lead, can I find it out?"
msgstr "Ma ei saa aru, kes juhib. Kust seda teada saada?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:456
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Yes, you can see statistics by opening the <guimenu>Game</guimenu> menu "
#| "and selecting <guimenuitem>Show Statistics</guimenuitem>."
msgid ""
"Yes, you can see statistics by opening the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Statistics</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Statistikat näeb siis, kui valida menüüst <guimenu>Mäng</guimenu> kirje "
"<guimenuitem>Näita statistikat</guimenuitem>."

